of Uzbekistan, 11 judges of the international category, 3 honored masters of sports of Uzbekistan, 36 international masters of sports, as well as champions and prize-winners Asian and international competitions, participants in the Olympic Games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Currently, the department conducts undergraduate lectures and practical classes in the following disciplines:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"301\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/ANG.jpg\" width=\"644\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>THE PUBLISHED LITERATURES BY PROFESSOR-TEACHERS </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"915\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(220).jpg\" width=\"626\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>COOPERATION RELATIONSHIPS OF THE DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"657\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Oqir%20Otletika/ANGagdgs.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>PROFESSOR-TEACHERS STRUCTURE </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"243\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Oqir%20Otletika/1.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Head of the department</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Orazimbetov Tolmas Aytimbetovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: <a href=\"mailto:talmas.urazimbetov@mail.ru\">talmas.urazimbetov@mail.ru</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"269\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Oqir%20Otletika/2.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pro