, dotsent S.P.Konov (1986-1987 yillar), O.A.Sobirova (1987-1998 yillar), E.M.Muminov (1998-1999 yillar), F.T.Ikramov (1999-2004 yillar), professor V.M.Korbut (2004-2018 yillar), 2018 yildan X.Yu.Matnazarov kafedra mudiri lavozimida ishlab kelmoqda.Kafedra tashkil topgan davrda suzish, suvga sakrash va suv polosi bo`yicha mashg&rsquo;ulotlar olib borildi. Keyinchalik kafedraga yangi fanlar tadbiq qilindi. 1976 yilda eshkak eshish ixtisosligi ochildi, 1990 yil dengiz ko`pkurashi ixtisosligi ochilib, 1996 yilda yopildi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"750\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/dsvsd.jpg\" width=\"1124\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Bugungi kunda kafedrada quyidagi fanlar bo`yicha ma`ruza, seminar va amaliy mashg`ulotlar olib borilmoqda:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"643\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(130).jpg\" width=\"781\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>PROFESSOR-O`QITUVCHILAR TOMONIDAN NASHR ETILGAN</strong>&nbsp;<strong>А</strong><strong>DABIYOTLAR:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"953\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(131).jpg\" width=\"663\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>KAFEDRANING&nbsp;</strong><strong>HAMKORLIK ALOQALARI</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"949\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(132).jpg\" 