a all-around and water sports&rdquo;, &ldquo;Swimming and rowing&rdquo;, &ldquo;Theories and methods of swimming, rowing and synchronized swimming&rdquo;.&nbsp;The first head of the department was V.F. Malykhin (1956-1957). Over the years, the department was headed by: V.N.Mikhailov (1957-1960), candidate of pedagogical sciences, associate professor L.Z. Gorokhovsky (1961-1969), honored trainer of Uzbekistan L.A. Filkov (1969-1971), candidate of biological sciences , Professor A.N. Livitsky (1972-1985), Candidate of Pedagogical Sciences, Associate Professor S.P. Konov (1986-1987), O.A.Sobirova (1987-1998), E.M. Muminov (1998-1999) , F.T. Ikramov (1999-2004), Professor V.M. Korbut (from 2004-2018), H.Yu. Matnazarov (from 2018 to the present).&nbsp;During the formation of the department, classes were held in the disciplines: swimming, diving, water polo. Then new disciplines were developed and introduced. In 1976, the specialization of rowing was opened, in 1990 - the specialization of all-around all-around (closed in 1996).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"750\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/dsvsd.jpg\" width=\"1124\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>TEACHED SUBJECTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"681\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(135).jpg\" width=\"831\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>SCIENTIFIC WORK PUBLISHED&nbsp;</strong><strong>PROFESSORIAL - TEACHING COMPOSITION OF THE DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"953\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0