n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/8jQ2CxQyzq96eCNuIVb1.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/10#\">УРИНБOЕВ ЭЛДOР АБДУРАСУЛOВИЧ</a>\r\n\r\n<div>Преподаватель кафедры</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;e-mail: e.o&rsquo;rinboyev@uzdjtsu.uz</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/ZhRoFwsvyadECnYKELNG.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/10#\">ТOЖИЕВ МУЗАФФАР АРБАРOВИЧ</a>\r\n\r\n<div>Преподаватель кафедры</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;e-mail: m.tojiyeve@uzdjtsu.uz</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n','<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"211\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/11.jpg\" style=\"float:left\" width=\"211\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Head of department:</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Umarov Djamshid Xasanovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Phone number:</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (90) 178-55-95</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>e-mail:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:j.umarov@uzdjtsu.u\">j.umarov@uzdjtsu.u</a>z</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The department of &ldquo;The theory and methodology of physical education, sport&rdquo; was founded in 1957. E.F. Ishchenko was the first head of it.During the period of the department, it was headed de the leading teacher-scientists they were the candidate of pedagogical sciences, docent K.F. Bakuniene, the candidate of p.s. docent I.M. Kolotilova, the candidate of p.s., docent K.M.Mahkamjonov, the candidate of p.s., professor R.S.Salomov,the candidate of Biologic sciences, professor Yu.M.Yunusova,&nbsp; the candidate of p.s., docent R.M. Matkarimov, the doctor of pedagogical sciences, professor F.A. Kerimov, the candidate of p.s., O.V.GoncharovaThe candidate of pedagogical sciences, docent D.X. Umarov have been controlling this department since November, in 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"688\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/IMG_0026.JPG\" width=\"1030\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The chair of &ldquo;The theory and methodology of physical education, sport&rdquo; has been working as an independent department since 1960.&nbsp;Its composition was filled with some experienced teachers such as N. Zisman, L. Polyakova, B. Roytburg in 1967. The candidate of pedagogical sciences, docent K. Bakuniene was controlled this department from 1960 to1967, he made a great contribution to its formation and development.&nbsp;For the 1st time, the lectures on &ldquo;The theory and methodology of physical education&rdquo; were taught in Uzbek language. The department was controlled by the candidate of pedagogical sciences, docent M. Godik (1967-1969), the candidate of biological sciences Yu.Yu. Yunusova (1972-1984) in different years. During this period the department was developed and achieved great successes.The leader specialists such as the doctor of pedagogical sciences, professor R.S.Salamov, the candidate of biological sciences T.T. Yunusov, the candidate of biological sciences Yu.Yu. Yunusova and the highly qualified teacher S.R. Daurenova, E.Yu. Daurenov, M.A. Mirodilov, L. Polyakova, E. Tarasova, SH.X. Isroilov worked there. In recent years the member of students has been grown significantly due to the organization of &ldquo;Professional education&rdquo; and &ldquo;Preschool and primary school education&rdquo; in bachelor&rsquo;s degree, the structure of the department &ldquo;The theory and methodology of physical education, sport&rdquo; has been also enriched.&nbsp; According to the Decree of the President of the Republic of Uzbekistan of march 5, 2018 &ldquo;On measures to improve the system of the Public Administration in the field of Physical education and sport on the basis of the Uzbek state Institute Physical education was renamed as the Uzbek state University Physical education and sport, and the department &ldquo;The theory and methodology of physical education&rdquo; was also changed into the department &ldquo;The theory and methodology of physical education and sport&rdquo;.The department has been got great of achievements by the right direction of academic &ndash; methodological.&nbsp;Scientific &ndash; research, spiritual &ndash; enlightment affairs.&nbsp;In particularly the Republican Olympiad on &ldquo;Theory and practice of Physical Education and Sport&rdquo; has been regularly organizing by this department.The senior teacher M. Mirjamolov successfully defended this dissertation paper and received a Ph. D degree on pedagogical sciences in 2017. So that, in 2017 the senior teacher of the department E. Raxmanov was awarded wish the title of &ldquo;The best pedagogue on the specialists on the educational field of the &ldquo;Service sphere&rdquo; at the Republican stage which was named with the best pedagogue of the higher educational institution by the Ministry of Higher and secondary Specialized Education.The doctor pedagogical science, professor F.A. Kerimov was awarded with the Order of &ldquo;Friendship&rdquo; by the decree of the President of the Republic of Uzbekistan on August, 2018.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:2pt\"><strong>Nowadays the department conducts lectures and practical exercises on following disciplines for bachelor degree students:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:2pt\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(33).png\" /></p