т и экономика”','DEPARTMENT OF SPORT MANAGEMENT AND ECONOMICS',NULL,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>KAFEDRA TARIXI</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Dastlab kafedrada &ldquo;Jismoniy tarbiya va sport menejmenti&rdquo;, &nbsp;&ldquo;Soliq va soliqqa tortish&rdquo;, &ldquo;Iqtisodiyot nazariyasi&rdquo;, &ldquo;Sport menejmenti&rdquo;, &ldquo;Sport marketingi&rdquo;, &ldquo;Sport iqtisodiyoti&rdquo;, &ldquo;Moliyaviy menejment&rdquo;,&nbsp; &ldquo;Sportda loyixalarni moliyalashtirish&rdquo; fanlari bo&lsquo;yicha mashg&lsquo;ulotlar olib borilgan. 2008 yilda kafedrada &ldquo;Jismoniy tarbiya va sport menejmenti&rdquo;&nbsp; magistratura mutaxassisligi ochilgan. Shu davrdan boshlab hozirgi kunga qadar ushbu mutaxassislikni tamomlagan 40 tadan ortiq mutaxassis kadrlar respublikamizning turli sport tashkilotlarida o&lsquo;z faoliyatlarini yuritib kelmoqdalar. 2011 yilda &quot;Iqtisodiyot va menejment&quot; kafedrasi &ldquo;Sport menejmenti va turizm&rdquo; nomi bilan qayta tashkil etilgan. 2014 yilga kelib kafedra &quot;Sport menejmenti va iqtisodiyot&quot; nomini oldi. Ushbu yillarda kafedra faoliyatini Z.T.G&lsquo;ulomov, A.A.Yadgarov, F.Yuldashev, Ye.S.Ablaeva va N.A.Abdievlar boshqarib kelgan. 2016 yildan hozirgi kunga qadar kafedraga iqtisod fanlari nomzodi, dotsent K.Sh.Ziyadullaev rahbarlik qilmoqda. Bundan tashqari O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi Prezidentining 2017 yil 20 apreldagi&nbsp; &ldquo;Oliy ta&rsquo;lim tizimini yanada rivojlantirish chora-tadbirlari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&rdquo;gi PQ-2909-son qarorining №25-ilovasiga muvofiq &ldquo;2017-2021 yillar davrida O&lsquo;zbekiston davlat jismoniy tarbiya institutining rivojlanish Dasturi&rdquo;ning ijrosini ta&rsquo;minlash maqsadida 2018-2019 o&lsquo;quv yilida &ldquo;Jismoniy tarbiya va sport menejmenti&rdquo;, &nbsp;2019-2020 o&lsquo;quv yilida &nbsp;esa &ldquo;Marketing (sport)&rdquo; bakalavriat ta&rsquo;lim yo&lsquo;nalishlari &nbsp;ochildi. 2017 yilda 5A610502 &ndash; &ldquo;Jismoniy tarbiya va sport menejmenti&rdquo; mutaxassisiligi bo&lsquo;yicha magistrant Sh.Erkinov dotsent K.Sh. Ziyadullaev rahbarligida &nbsp;Prezident stipendiyasining sohibi bo&lsquo;ldi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/1.jpg\" width=\"591\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Bugungi kunda bakalavriat va magistratura talabalariga kafedrada quyidagi fanlar bo&lsquo;yicha mashg&lsquo;ulotlar olib borilmoqda.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"351\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/%D0%91%D0%B5%D0%B7%D1%8B%D0%BC%D1%8F%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B9.png\" width=\"566\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Magistratura talabalariga quyidagi fanlar o&lsquo;qitiladi.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"104\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/%D0%91%D0%B5%D0%B7%D1%8B%D0%BC%D1%8F%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B91.png\" width=\"566\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Professor-o&lsquo;qituvchilar tarkibi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"209\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/photo_2021-06-19_11-44-24.jpg\" width=\"314\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kafedra mudiri, dotsent,&nbsp; iqtisod fanlari nomzodi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ziyadullaev Komil Shamsievich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: komilz@inbox.ru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"159\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/7.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kafedra professori,&nbsp; iqtisod fanlari doktori</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikramov Murat Akramovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail:ikramov.m@mail.ru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"184\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/2.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>O&lsquo;qituvchi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mamatov Mirziyod Normurot o&lsquo;g&lsquo;li</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: menejment_mamatov<a href=\"mailto:abdiev@uz-djti.uz\">@uz-djti.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"182\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/4.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>O&lsquo;qituvchi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yusupov &nbsp;Zulunjon Ziyoydinovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: menejment_yusupov<a href=\"mailto:abdiev@uz-djti.uz\">@uz-djti.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"212\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/5.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>O&lsquo;qituvchi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rasulov Аnvar Saidmurod oʼgʼli</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: <a href=\"mailto:аnvarrasulov1199@gmail.com\">аnvarrasulov1199@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:аnvarrasulov1199@gmail.com\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/6.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>O&lsquo;qituvchi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rashidov Azizbek Ulug&lsquo;bekovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: menejment_rashidov<a href=\"mailto:abdiev@uz-djti.uz\">@uz-djti.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"133\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/3.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>O&lsquo;qituvchi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Babajanov Rustam Yuldashovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: rustambabajanov84@mail.ru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"246\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/8.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kafedra&nbsp; dotsenti,&nbsp; iqtisod fanlari nomzodi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Narziev Jalalitdin Paygamovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: menejment_<a href=\"mailto:narziev@uz-djti.uz\">narziev@uz-djti.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"133\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/photo_2021-06-19_11-45-05.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kafedra&nbsp; dotsenti,&nbsp; iqtisod fanlari nomzodi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Axmedov Ikrom Akramovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail:i.axmedov2@uzdjtsu.uz</p>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>ИСТОРИЯ КАФЕДРЫ</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Первоначально на кафедре велись занятия по дисциплинам &laquo;Менеджмент физической культуры и спорта&raquo;, &laquo;Налоги и налогообложение&raquo;, &laquo;Экономическая теория&raquo;, &laquo;Спортивный менеджмент&raquo;, &laquo;Спортивный маркетинг&raquo;, &laquo;Экономика спорта&raquo;, &laquo;Финансовый менеджмент&raquo;, &laquo;Финансирование &nbsp;проектов в спорте&raquo;. В 2008 году кафедрой была открыта специальность по магистратуре &laquo;Менеджмент физической культуры и спорта&raquo;. С тех пор более 40 специалистов, окончивших эту специальность, работают в различных спортивных организациях страны. В 2011 году кафедра &ldquo;Экономика и менеджмент&rdquo; была реорганизована в кафедру с названием &laquo;Спортивный менеджмент и туризм&raquo;. В 2014 году кафедра была переименована в &laquo;Спортивный менеджмент и экономика&raquo;. В эти годы кафедру возглавляли З.Т. Гулямов, А.А. Ядгаров, Ф. Юлдашев, Е.С. Аблаева и Н.А. Абдиев. С 2016 года по настоящее время кафедру возглавляет кандидат экономических наук, доцент К.Ш.Зиядуллаев. В соответствии с Приложением № 25 &ldquo;Программа развития Узбекского государственного института физической культуры на период 2017-2021 года&rdquo; Постановления Президента Республики Узбекистан от 20 апреля 2017 года&nbsp; ПҚ-2909 &laquo;О мерах по дальнейшему развитию системы высшего образования&raquo;, в 2018-2019 учебном году было открыто направление в бакалавриате &ldquo;Менеджмент физической культуры и спорта&rdquo;, а 2019-2020 учебном году &nbsp;&laquo;Маркетинг (спорт)&raquo;. В 2017 году магистр по специальности 5A610502 &ndash; &ldquo;Менеджмент физической культуры и спорта&rdquo; Эркинов Ш. под научном руководством доцента Зиядуллаева К.Ш. &nbsp;стал обладателем президентской стипендии.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/asfasfasdf.jpg\" width=\"676\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>В НАСТОЯЩЕЕ ВРЕМЯ СТУДЕНТЫ И МАГИСТРАНТЫ ОБУЧАЮТСЯ ПО СЛЕДУЮЩИМ ДИСЦИПЛИНАМ.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"412\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/%D0%A0%D0%A3%D0%A1%D0%A1%D0%A7%D0%90%201.png\" width=\"663\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>МАГИСТРАНТАМ ПРЕПОДАЮТСЯ СЛЕДУЮЩИЕ ДИСЦИПЛИНЫ:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"121\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/%D0%A0%D0%A3%D0%A1%D0%A1%D0%A7%D0%90%202.png\" width=\"663\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>ПРОФЕССОРСКО-ПРЕПОДАВАТЕЛЬСКИЙ СОСТАВ</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Professor-o&lsquo;qituvchilar tarkibi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"209\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/photo_2021-06-19_11-44-24.jpg\" width=\"314\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Заведующий кафедрой, доцент,&nbsp; кандидат экономических наук</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Зиядуллаев Комил Шамсиевич</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: komilz@inbox.ru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"159\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/7.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Профессор, кандидат экономических наук</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Икрамов Мурат Акрамович</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail:ikramov.m@mail.ru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"184\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/2.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Преподаватель</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Маматов Мирзиёд Нормурот ўғли</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: menejment_mamatov<a href=\"mailto:abdiev@uz-djti.uz\">@uz-djti.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"182\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/4.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Преподаватель</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Юсупов &nbsp;Зулунжон Зиёйдинович</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: menejment_yusupov<a href=\"mailto:abdiev@uz-djti.uz\">@uz-djti.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"212\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/5.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Преподаватель</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Расулов Анвар Саидмурод ўғли</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: <a href=\"mailto:аnvarrasulov1199@gmail.com\">аnvarrasulov1199@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:аnvarrasulov1199@gmail.com\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/6.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Преподаватель</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Рашидов Азизбек Улуғбекович</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: menejment_rashidov<a href=\"mailto:abdiev@uz-djti.uz\">@uz-djti.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"133\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/3.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Преподаватель</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Бабажанов Рустам Юлдашович</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: rustambabajanov84@mail.ru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"246\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/Menejment/8.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Доцент, кандидат экономических наук</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Нарзиев Жалалитдин Пайгамович</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail: menejment_<a href=\"mailto:narziev@uz-djti.uz\">narziev@uz-djti.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"133\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/photo_2021-06-19_11-45-05.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Доцент, кандидат экономических наук</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ахмедов Икром Акрамович</p>\r\n\r\n<p>E-mail:i.axmedov2@uzdjtsu.uz</p>\r\n','<div style=\"margin-left:-30px;\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"250\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/.jpg6.jpg\" style=\"float:left\" width=\"250\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>Head of&nbsp; department</strong><strong>:</strong>&nbsp;Ziyadullaev Komil Shamsiyevich</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;Telephone</strong><strong>:</strong>&nbsp;(93) 532-48-10</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>E-mail:</strong>&nbsp;<u>komilz@inbox.ru</u>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Department of Economics and Management was established in 2008 under the Uzbek State University of&nbsp;&nbsp;Physical Education and Sport.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HISTORY OF THE DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Initially, the department taught courses in &quot;Physical Education and Sport Management&quot;, &quot;Taxes and Taxation&quot;, &quot;Economic Theory&quot;, &quot;Sport Management&quot;, &quot;Sport Marketing&quot;, &quot;Sport Economics&quot;, &quot;Financial Management&quot;, &quot; Financing Projects in Sport &quot;.&nbsp;In 2008, the department opened Master&rsquo;s Degree on &quot;Physical Training and Sport Management&quot;. More than 40 cadres who have graduated from this specialty are working at various sports organizations of the country.&nbsp;In 2011, the Department of Economics and Management was reorganized as &quot;Sport Management and Tourism&quot;. In 2014, the department was renamed &quot;Sport Management and Economics&quot;. During these years the department was headed by Z.T. Gulomov, A.A. Yadgarov, F. Yuldashev, E.S. Ablaeva and N.A. Abdiev. From 2016 till these days department is headed by Candidate of Economic Sciences, Associate Professor K. Ziyadullaev.&nbsp;Besides, in accordance with Appendix N 25 to the Resolution of the President of the Republic of Uzbekistan dated on April 20, 2017 N PP-2909 &quot;On measures for further development of the higher education system&quot;, in 2018-2019 academic year were opened undergraduate courses on &quot;Physical Education and Sport Management&quot; and in the 2019-2020 academic years &quot;Marketing (Sports)&quot;&nbsp;In 2017, one of our student who studied on Master&rsquo;s specialty 5A610502 - &ldquo;Management of physical education and sports&rdquo; Erkinov Sh. became the owner of a presidential scholarship under the scientific supervision of associate professor Ziyadullaev K.Sh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/.jpg7.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nowadays undergraduate and graduate students study the following disciplines:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"619\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(110).jpg\" width=\"733\" />&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Master degree</strong><strong>&nbsp;students study the following disciplines:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"178\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(110)%D1%80%D1%80%D1%80.jpg\" width=\"725\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Until this day teachers of the department have published 2 books, 2 manuals,&nbsp; 38 methodical instructions and instructions, and more than 400 scientific articles and theses on Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree in Physical Education and Sport Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>THE TEACHING STAFF</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The department has 13 staff units, including the head of the department, 3 professors, 6 associate professors, 4 senior teachers and 8 teachers. The scientific potential of the department is 48%.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LITERATURES THAT PUBLISHED BY PROFESSOR-TEACHERS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"1022\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(107).jpg\" width=\"779\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COOPERATIONS OF THE DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From November 17 to November 24, 2018 in the framework of cooperation with the Department of Sport Management and Economics of the Ural State University of Russian Federation, Associate Professor of this department T.V. Mikhaillenko organized a scientific seminar on &quot;Effective usage of foreign experience in the field of physical culture and sports&quot;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"872\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(109).jpg\" width=\"1210\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From October 7 till October 10 of 2019 year in collaboration with the French Embassy in Uzbekistan, professor Gary Tribou of the University of Strasbourg, France, held a scientific seminar on &quot;Sport Marketing and its Key Features&quot;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"696\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(115)1.jpg\" width=\"966\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h4>Head of the department</h4>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/June2019/P2vpY4SeXDMCKY8Or079.jpg\" wid