Asia and Europe competitions.They are: S.Diamidov, E.Saadi,O.Aibinder, I.Baraksanova, Ya.Batirshina, E.Levochkina,G.Nedoihleb, D.Polarush, V.Semenchuk, L.Cherazova, O.Chusovitina,<br />\r\nA.Fokin and many others.&nbsp;Rhythmic sportive gymnastics has become very popular during independence of our country. And in 2005 specialization of Rhythmic sportive gymnasticswas organized in our faculty.&nbsp;A.Yefimenko, N.Fethulova, A.Eshtaev, B.Musaev, G.Hasanova, S.Eshtaev, J.Umarov, M.Davurbaeva have defended their theses during the period of&nbsp;&nbsp;our Independence.&nbsp;The young specialists continue their scientific investigations and get ready for defense of their doctor&rsquo;s theses (PhD,DSc),participate in Republic and International Conferences.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"632\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/hgf.jpg\" width=\"672\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TOUGHT BRANCHES OF SCIENCE</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(160).jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>At present the faculty has being held lectures and seminars for Master&rsquo;s degree students on the subject</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(160)gg.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SCIENTIFIC STAFF OF THE FACULTY&nbsp;</strong><strong>PROFFESSORATE-TEACHING STAFF</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At present there are six docents, eight senior teachers and twenty-three teachers work in our faculty.There are five science candidates and two philosophy doctors(PhD).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SCIENTIFIC WORKS OF THE TEACHER STAFF</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"630\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(155).jpg\" width=