p>x.toshpulatov@uzdjtsu.uz</p>\r\n\r\n<div><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/DrCJ0JOYr03ScRLHMVBn.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Преподаватель кафедры</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div><a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">ИБРАГИМОВ ФОЗИЛЖОН ЗОХИРЖОНОВИЧ</a></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/InNcvu0Bhb9JdZSYu7n2.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Преподаватель кафедры</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">ТУНЬЯН АЛЁНА АНДРЕЕВНА</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-mail: a.tunyan@uzdjtsu.uz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/pk06h3mIA1Bvc6OsY4Ai.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Преподаватель кафедры</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">ПУЛАТОВ ФАРХОД АЗАДОВИЧ</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>f.pulatov@uzdjtsu.uz</p>\r\n\r\n<div><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/WsD2fIXGb48n9B8DVKd6.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Преподаватель кафедры</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">КУБЕЙСИНОВА УЛБОСЫН ТУРСУНБАЕВНА</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>volleyball007@uzdjtsu.uz</p>\r\n\r\n<div><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/q2X29pespnqxndd6oGIo.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Преподаватель кафедры</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">ПРЕПОДАВАТЕЛЬ КАФЕДРЫ</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-mail: sh.nurmatova@uzdjtsu.uz</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/AODK46lbRweQqImKHCCL.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Преподаватель кафедры</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">АБАТОВА ГУЛЬЗАР НУРЛАН ҚИЗИ</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>g.abatova@uzdjtsu.uz</p>\r\n</div>\r\n','<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"250\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/.jpg5.jpg\" style=\"float:left\" width=\"250\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>Head of chair</strong><strong>:&nbsp;</strong>Ashurkova Svetlana Fedorovna</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Phone</strong><strong>:</strong>&nbsp;(93)&nbsp;396 72 19</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;E-mail:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:s.ashurkova@uzdjtsu.uz\">s.ashurkova@uzdjtsu.uz</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>THE HISTORY OF THE DEPARTMENT&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The department of sports was created in 1955, in the year of formation of institute, with functional purpose on training of highly qualified specialists in volleyball, basketball, soccer, tennis, handball and swimming. In 1956-57 academic year from the structure of department specialization - swimming was allocated. In 1959 the republic for the first time received 36 experts with the higher education: on volleyball &ndash; 9, on basketball &ndash; 11, on soccer &ndash; 15 and on tennis &ndash; 1 which in the subsequent were distributed for work in the specialty to various regions of Uzbekistan. In 2000 the department received the new name - &quot;Department of Sports and National Games&quot;. Since 2018 with acquisition of the status the university the name of department &ndash; &quot;Theory and Technique of Volleyball, Basketball&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/5555.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The honored coach of Uzbekistan of Cords of V.H. who headed it till 1960 was the first head of the department of sports from the date of foundation of institute (1955).&nbsp;In various years managed department: Keshishev G.L. &ndash; honored coach of Uzbekistan (1960-1968), Shveduks V.F. &ndash; honored coach of Uzbekistan (1968-1970), Itskov R.I. &ndash; honored coach of Uzbekistan (1970-1972), Rasulev A.T. &ndash; professor (1972-1974), Kasymov A.Sh. &ndash; the associate professor (1974-1984), Ayrapetyants L.R. is the professor, the honored coach of Uzbekistan (1984 - 2016), Kdyrova M.A. &ndash; to. item of N, associate professor (2016-2018), Ashurkova S. F. &ndash; the world class master of sports on volleyball (2018-till present). The volleyball, basketball and tennis national teams showed good results as at intra republican competitions (the championships, the Federation Cup, the Cup of Uzbekistan, &quot;Universiade&quot;), and the international tournaments in recent years owing to what the first world class masters of sports of the Republic of Uzbekistan appeared.The faculty of department prepared and published 13 monographs, more than 20 textbooks, 120 manuals, 300 methodical grants, 200 methodical recommendations, 600 scientific articles and theses. The scientific products of the faculty of department are regularly published in scientific publications of institute, magazines and collections of the scientific works published in Uzbekistan, the CIS countries and foreign countries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"656\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(236).jpg\" width=\"920\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CURRENT PROFESSOR-TEACHING STAFF OF THE DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Education, scientific degree, title and specialization of the teaching staff of the department corresponds to the specialization of the department. Currently, the department of theory and methodology of volleyball, basketball taught 1 professor, 2 associate professors, 1 candidate of pedagogical sciences, 5 senior teachers, 10 teachers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LITERATURE PUBLISHED BY THE FACULTY OF THE DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"1033\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(100).jpg\" width=\"733\" />&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"1010\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(101).jpg\" width=\"613\" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COOPERATION OF THE DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/departments/December2019/%20%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0%20(229).jpg\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h4>Head of the department</h4>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/July2019/rZk6wJiPRYfKf81aFp6o.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">ASHURKOVA SVETLANA FEDOROVNA</a>\r\n\r\n<div>Head of the department</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Monday - Saturday 14:00-17:00</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;(93) 396 72 19</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;s.ashurkova@uzdjtsu.uz</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>Teachers</h3>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/SOSrsHYA2LBiBlxuQhLB.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">PULATOV AZAD ARTIKOVICH</a>\r\n\r\n<div>Associate professor of the department</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;a.pulatov@uzdjtsu.uz</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/storage/teachers/December2019/tlcvWbuuLMOnSXPwP3wX.jpg\" width=\"170\" /></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://uzdjtsu.uz/department/17#\">KDIROVA MUKHABBAT ALLANIYAZOVNA</a>\