n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"304\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/1.jpg\" width=\"230\" /></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Маткаримов Гайрат Рахимберганович</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<div>Старший преподаватель</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Приемные дни вторник-пятница: 14: 00-17:00</div>\r\n\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"303\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/14584.png\" width=\"230\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Дилмуродов Шухрат Сафарович</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>преподаватель</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Приемные дни вторник-пятница: 14: 00-17:00</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n','<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">ABOUT THE DEPARTMENT &quot; THEORY AND METHODOLOGY OF BOXING, FENCING</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Since 2021, at the Department of&rdquo; Theory and Methodology of Boxing, Fencing&quot;, Doctor of Ph. D. (PhD) Serebryakov Yuri Vladimirovich holds the position of head of the Department. The Department of &quot;Theory and Methodology of Boxing, Fencing&quot; is a structural division of the Faculty of Martial Arts.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Reception hours: Monday 14: 00-17: 00; Saturday 15: 00-17: 00;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Phone: 9978673115</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Email: DEPARTMENT</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">HISTORY</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">The Uzbek State University of Physical Culture and Sports is one of the largest institutions in Central Asia that trains highly qualified specialists in the field of physical culture and sports in Uzbekistan. The institute was originally founded in August 1955. In 1958, the Department of Boxing, Wrestling and Weightlifting was established. And Yu. I. Sirotkin was appointed as the head of the department.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Among the graduates and teachers of the department, most have the degree of Doctor of Pedagogical Sciences and professor: Sh. A. Abdullaev, G. B. Abdurasulov, V. Alekseenko, Sh. N. Zokirov, Z. T.Kosimbekov, A. Rafikova, I. Sadriddinov, M. I. Sidikov, F. K.Turdiev, V. N. Shin, A. A. Kodirov, R. A. Maksimov, H. I. Mukhammedov, B. N. Nazarov, T. Pulatov, I. Yu. Shamsutdinov, A. S. Gelyugen, (boxing), K. A. Tazhieva, O. A. Zaburnyagin, L. I. Efremova, P. A. Kutelinas, V. Mikhailov, E. N. Sokolova, N. A. Fetisov, (fencing) for many years conducted their activities at the department.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Since 2008, in connection with the addition of the specialty &ldquo;Taekwondo WTF&rdquo; to the department, the department has been called &ldquo;Theory and methodology of boxing, fencing and taekwondo&rdquo;.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">In 2017, by the decree of the President, the Uzbek State Institute of Physical Culture was granted the status of a university, and the department was renamed &quot;theory and methodology of boxing, taekwondo, fencing&quot;.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Since February 1, 2021, the department has been called &quot; Theory and methodology of Boxing, fencing&raquo;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Currently, the composition of professors and teachers has high greetings, in which doctors of Sciences, Prof. R. D. Khalmukhamedov, Prof. S. S. Tazhibayev, Ph. D. A. T. Abdullayev, Razhabov G. K., Yu.V.Serebryakov, senior teachers: A. U. Ibragimov, K. A. Umarov, D. Sh. Kalandarov, R. N. Abdukhamidov, V. D. Anashov, Sh. K. Karimov, Matkarimov G. R. Teachers: K. S. Abdullayev, Dilmuradov Sh. S., Yuldashev F. S. T. Usmonkhodjaev.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">The department constantly cooperates with the related departments of the Institutes of Physical Culture of the South Korean state and the Commonwealth of Independent States.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">In the future, the department plans to create a research laboratory equipped with scientific and medical equipment for conducting research.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Teaching staff:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">The basic education of the teaching staff of the department, the academic degree,</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">and the specialties of scientific titles correspond to the specialization of the department.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">The department has 17.5 employees, of which 1 head of the department, 2</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">professors, 1 associate professor, 6 senior teachers, 12</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">work as a teacher in the main staff.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"308\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/548454.png\" width=\"230\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Serebryakov Yuriy Vladimirovich</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:4.4pt\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">Head of the Department Doctor of Ph. D. (PhD)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">Reception days: Tuesday 14: 00-17: 00 Friday: 14: 00-17: 00</span></pre>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"145\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/1212121.jpg\" width=\"230\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Xalmuxamedov Rustam Dekanovich</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">DSP rofessor&nbsp;Professor</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif