f the Rector and other regulations.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Main functions of department</strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\"><strong>:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;The educational-methodical department organizes the educational process in accordance with the duly approved state educational standards, curricula and working curricula, standard and working-class programs in the disciplines, on the basis of which lesson plans are developed. and ensures its full implementation by all faculties and departments;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Coordinates the activities of faculties, departments and other structural units involved in the educational process;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Works systematically to improve state educational standards, curricula, science programs in each field of study and master&#39;s specialties in accordance with the experience of developed countries and modern requirements. It also identifies standards that do not&nbsp; work well during the implementation of regulations and prepares appropriate recommendations and suggestions for their further improvement;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The department, together with the dean&#39;s office, monitors the implementation of the current rating system of assessment, quality control of teaching, student learning.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Studies, summarizes and implements modern information, pedagogical technologies and practical experiences that use in Uzbekistan and abroad.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Supervises the writing of course work, dissertations, master&#39;s dissertations on the development of sports, problems in sports and ways to solve them.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Together with the faculties and departments, reviews the working curricula, curricula and working programs, textbooks, manuals, other types of educational and methodological documents and provide educational materials for recommendation or approval by the Academic Council.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Supervises the provision of students with curricula and other teaching materials by the departments.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Reviews and plans the distribution of workloads performed by professor-teachers of the University, as well as the staffing schedule of them;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Identifies the volume and composition of teaching load, educational-methodical, research and organizational-methodological work that must be performed by professor-teachers, Heads of Departments and Deans of Faculties of the University during the academic year based on the norms of time, and submits to the Academic Council for approval</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Monitors the implementation of planned workloads at the departments, draws up and formalize documents for full-time and part-time professor-teachers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Reviews and accepts the annual reports of the departments, professors-teachers, as well as participate in the preparation of the annual general report of the University.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Organizes open classes to facilitate the exchange of experiences between the professor-teachers and students;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Takes measures to implement the decisions of the Academic Council in the educational process.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Plans all the organizational work for the graduation theses and defense of master&#39;s dissertations. Prepares the necessary documents for the organization of the work of the State Attestation Commission and sends them to University departments, Dean`s offices and Heads of the Chair, supervises the work of the State Attestation Commission, execution of reports of the State Attestation Commission on time and submission to the Educational-Methodological Department.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Organizes seminars to improve the skills of professor-teachers of&nbsp; the Department in modern pedagogical and information technologies, as well as foreign languages.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Monitors constantly the educational-methodological processes of the University Departments, Deans of the Faculties, make suggestions for improving the educational-methodological work and submit them to the Academic Council.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:times new roman,times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Regularly monitors the correctness of students&#39; personal documents, recording students` grades and other similar documents in the Dean&#39;s Office.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"209\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/photo_2021-06-19_11-44-57.jpg\" width=\"314\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;THE HEAD OF DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Raxmanov Eldor Tolibjonovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phone<strong>:</strong> +998 (94) 678-83-23</p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-mail: ret.0210@mail.ru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"236\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/%D0%9E%D0%9A%D0%A3%D0%92%20%D0%91%D0%9E%D0%9B%D0%98%D0%9C/%D0%91%D0%B5%D0%B7%D1%8B%D0%BC%D1%8F%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B9111212.jpg\" width=\"314\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DEPUTY HEAD OF &nbsp;DEPARTMENT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rozikov Jasurbek Masharibovich<strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phone: +998 (99) 407-77-67</p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-mail: jas.07@mail.ru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"267\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/%D0%9E%D0%9A%D0%A3%D0%92%20%D0%91%D0%9E%D0%9B%D0%98%D0%9C/%D0%91%D0%B5%D0%B7%D1%8B%D0%BC%D1%8F%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B9.jpg\" width=\"314\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;METHODIST</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alfayzov Salohiddin Abdusalomovich</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phone: +998 (99) 847-13-18</p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-mail: <a href=\"mailto:saloxiddinalfayzov@mail.ru\">saloxiddinalfayzov@mail.ru</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"216\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/%D0%9E%D0%9A%D0%A3%D0%92%20%D0%91%D0%9E%D0%9B%D0%98%D0%9C/%D0%91%D0%B5%D0%B7%D1%8B.jpg\" width=\"314\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;METHODIST</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yuldoshev Ulug&lsquo;bek Asqar o&lsquo;g&lsquo;li</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phone: +998 (97) 740-16-66</p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-mail:&nbsp;u.yuldoshevtsue@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/%D0%9E%D0%9A%D0%A3%D0%92%20%D0%91%D0%9E%D0%9B%D0%98%D0%9C/%D0%91%D0%B5%D0%B7%D1%8B000.jpg\" width=\"314\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; INSPECTOR</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kasimova Umida Xamidovna</p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-mail<strong>:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"mailto:umida.110590@mail.ru\">umida.110590@mail.ru</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"255\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/test/%D0%9E%D0%9A%D0%A3%D0%92%20%D0%91%D0%9E%D0%9B%D0%98%D0%9C/%D0%91%D0%B5%D0%B7%D1%8B000333.jpg\" width=\"314\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; DISPETCHER</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yulchiyeva Dilafruz Abduvali qizi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-mail:<strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"mailto:umidjon.2706@mail.ru\">umidjon.2706@mail.ru</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'unnamed.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": \"\", \"meta_des_2\": \"\", \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null,