n&nbsp;jarayonlarini xolis va adolatli o&lsquo;tkazish masalasiga bag&lsquo;ishlangan yig&lsquo;ilish bo&lsquo;lib o&lsquo;tdi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Yig&lsquo;ilishda O&lsquo;zbekiston davlat jismoniy tarbiya va sport universiteti rektori, Qabul komissiyasi raisi M. Boltabayev, Toshkent viloyati Chirchiq shahar ichki ishlar 3-sonli bo&lsquo;lim boshlig&lsquo;i I. Tursunov va universitet prorektorlari, fakultet dekanlari, dekan o&lsquo;rinbosarlari, kafedra mudirlari, qabul komissiyasi aʼzolari ishtirok etishdi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Tadbirda so&lsquo;z olganlar oliy taʼlim tizimida ishlashning o&lsquo;ziga xos sharafli va mashaqqatli jihatlari haqida gapirib, har bir xodim ana shu sharafga, el-yurtning hurmatiga munosib bo&lsquo;lishi kerakligi haqida to&lsquo;xtalib o&lsquo;tdilar.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Shuningdek, soha xodimlari orasida uchrayotgan ayrim salbiy holatlar haqida misollar keltirildi. Bu misollardan to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri xulosa chiqarib, xizmat intizomini mustahkamlash, korrupsiya va tamagirlik kabi illatlarning oldini olish borasida zarur maslahat va tavsiyalar berildi.</span></p>\r\n','<p>7 июля текущего года в Узбекском государственном университете физической культуры и спорта совместно с отделом внутренних дел города Чирчик состоялось совещание с участием сотрудников университета по вопросам укрепления служебной дисциплины и законности, беспристрастного и справедливого проведения творческих экзаменов.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>На заседании приняли участие ректор Узбекского государственного университета физической культуры и спорта, председатель приемной комиссии М. Болтабаев, начальник отдела № 3 Чирчикского городского отдела внутренних дел Ташкентской области И. Турсунов, проректоры университета, деканы факультетов, заместители деканов, заведующие кафедрами, члены приемной комиссии.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Выступившие на мероприятии рассказали об особенностях и трудностях работы в системе высшего образования и отметили, что каждый сотрудник должен быть достойным этой чести, уважения народа и страны.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Также были приведены примеры некоторых негативных ситуаций, с которыми сталкиваются работники данной отрасли. Из этих примеров были сделаны правильные выводы, даны необходимые советы и рекомендации по укреплению служебной дисциплины, предотвращению таких пороков, как коррупция и вымогательство.</p>\r\n','<p>The 7 of June of Present year organized the meeting dedicated to purely and fairly organizing the creative exams, also strengthening the work discipline and legitimacy with the participation of university staff.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rector of the Uzbek State University of Physical Education and Sports, Chairman of the Admissions Committee M. Boltabayev, Head of the Department of Internal Affairs No. 3 of Chirchik, Tashkent region I. Tursunov and</p>\r\n\r\n<p>vice-rectors, deans of faculties, deputy deans, also the heads of departments and members of Admission Committee took part in the meeting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speakers at the event spoke about the unique honors and challenges of working in the higher education system, emphasizing that every employee should be worthy of this honor and respect of the people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Examples were also given of some of the negative situations encountered among industry workers. Drawing the right conclusions from these examples, the necessary advice and recommendations were given to strengthen service discipline and prevent corruption and greed.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": \"\", \"meta_des_2\": \"\", \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_2\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1625598000,NULL,1625834397,1625851052,215,293,1,1,1625834397,1625834397,1625834397,1625834397),(168,1,'sportchilarni-tayyorlash-tizimini-rivojlantirish-masalalari-ko-rib-chiqildi','Sportchilarni tayyorlash tizimini rivojlantirish masalalari ko‘rib chiqildi','','',NULL,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Sportchilarni tayyorlash tizimini rivojlantirish masalalari ko&lsquo;rib chiqildi</strong></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Prezident Shavkat Mirziyoyev 9-iyul kuni sport taʼlimini rivojlantirish va Olimpiya zaxiralarini tayyorlash masalalariga doir taqdimot bilan tanishdi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Bugungi kunda mamlakatimizda 15 ta olimpiya zaxiralari kolleji, 344 ta sport maktabi va 7 ta oliy sport mahorati maktabi faoliyat yuritmoqda. Ularda 380 ming nafar yoshlar 100 dan ortiq sport turi bilan muntazam shug&lsquo;ullanmoqda.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">So&lsquo;nggi uch yilda Olimpiya zaxiralari kollejlari o&lsquo;quvchilari xalqaro musobaqalarda 723 ta, respublika turnirlarida 10 mingdan ziyod medallarni qo&lsquo;lga kiritgan. Qariyb 4 ming 500 nafar o&lsquo;quvchi O&lsquo;zbekiston milliy terma jamoalariga qabul qilingan.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Bu sohani yana-da rivojlantirish uchun sport taʼlimi muassasalarining moddiy-texnik bazasini mustahkamlash, murabbiylar malakasini oshirish zarur.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Xususan, ushbu muassasalarda ishlayotgan 14 mingga yaqin murabbiylarning qariyb 6 ming nafari oliy maʼlumotga ega emas. Shuningdek, joylarda ot sporti, zamonaviy besh kurash, regbi, o&lsquo;q otish, kamondan otish, velosport, suvga sakrash va sinxron suzish bo&lsquo;yicha murabbiylar yetishmaydi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Taqdimotda sport taʼlimi tizimini tubdan yaxshilash, zamonaviy dastur va metodikalarni joriy etish, muassasalarning moddiy-texnik bazasini rivojlantirish masalalari ko&lsquo;rib chiqildi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Davlatimiz rahbari Olimpiya zaxiralari kollejlari hamda jismoniy tarbiya va sport yo&lsquo;nalishidagi oliy taʼlim muassasalari infratuzilmasini yaxshilab, sport taʼlimini takomillashtirish, o&lsquo;quvchi va talabalar sonini oshirish bo&lsquo;yicha topshiriqlar berdi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sohadagi taʼlim muassasalarining Paralimpiya bo&lsquo;limlariga 10 foizgacha qo&lsquo;shimcha kvota ajratilishi hamda ota-onalar tomonidan to&lsquo;lov tartibi bekor qilinishi belgilandi. Shuningdek, qizlar uchun kvotani ko&lsquo;paytirish orqali Xalqaro olimpiya qo&lsquo;mitasining gender tenglikka doir tamoyillari taʼminlanadi.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Seleksiya ishlarini kuchaytirish, bu jarayonda ochiqlik va shaffoflikni taʼminlab, korrupsiya holatlariga barham berish bo&lsquo;yicha ko&lsquo;rsatmalar berildi. Olimpiya zaxiralari kollejlariga o&lsquo;quvchilarni qabul qilish, iqtidorli sportchilarni saralash va musobaqalar tashkil etish bo&lsquo;yicha elektron platformani ishga tushirish vazifasi qo&lsquo;yildi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Prezidentimiz Olimpiya zaxiralari kollejlarini sport federatsiyalari bilan uzviy bog&lsquo;lash, iqtidorli yoshlarni o&lsquo;stirishda promouter, skaut, agent kabi mutaxassislar faoliyatini keng qo&lsquo;llash va bu yo&lsquo;nalishlarni rivojlantirish muhimligini taʼkidladi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Sportchilarning jismoniy, tibbiy va psixologik holatini hamda farmakologik taʼminotini yaxshilash bo&lsquo;yicha topshiriqlar berildi. Sportchilarni tayyorlash va o&lsquo;quv muassasalarini boshqarish tizimini ilmiy asoslangan ravishda rivojlantirish zarurligi aytildi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2021-2022 o&lsquo;quv yilidan boshlab, sport maktablarida davlat buyurtmasi asosida razryadli va unvonli sportchilarni tayyorlash yo&lsquo;lga qo&lsquo;yilishi belgilandi.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Murabbiylar yetishmayotgan sport turlari bo&lsquo;yicha malakali xorijiy mutaxassislarni jalb qilish, ularga mahalliy murabbiy va talabalarni biriktirib, tajribasini o&lsquo;rganish kerakligi qayd etildi.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;Sport taʼlimi muassasalarini qurish va taʼmirlash, zamonaviy jihozlar va sport adabiyotlari bilan taʼminlash bo&lsquo;yicha ham ko&lsquo;rsatmalar berildi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Olimpiya va Paralimpiya o&lsquo;yinlariga tayyorgarlik masalalariga ham eʼtibor qaratildi. Sportchilarimiz Yaponiya poytaxti Tokio shahrida bo&lsquo;lib o&lsquo;tadigan ushbu nufuzli musobaqaga jami 126 ta yo&lsquo;llanmani qo&lsquo;lga kiritgan.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Davlatimiz rahbari sportchi va murabbiylarni har tomonlama qo&lsquo;llab-quvvatlash, yaxshi natijalarga erishishi uchun barcha sharoitlarni yaratish zarurligini taʼkidladi. Shu bilan birga, 2024-yili Fransiyada bo&lsquo;lib o&lsquo;tadigan Olimpiya o&lsquo;yinlariga tayyorgarlikni hozirdan boshlash bo&lsquo;yicha ko&lsquo;rsatmalar berdi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://minsport.uz/oz/news/tag/none-551\"><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">#Shavkat Mirziyoyev</span></a></p>\r\n','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": \"\", \"meta_des_2\": \"\", \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_2\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1625770800,NULL,1625849856,1628500377,217,67,1,1,1625849856,1625849856,1625849856,1625849856),(169,1,'hurmatli-ota-onalar-va-abituriyentlar-diqqatiga','HURMATLI OTA-ONALAR VA ABITURIYENTLAR DIQQATIGA!','','',NULL,NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">? Oliy va o&lsquo;rta maxsus taʼlim vaziri Abduqodir Toshqulov hamda vazir o&lsquo;rinbosarlarining murojaatlar platformasi ishga tushganligi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida xabar bergan edik (<a href=\"https://t.me/eduuz/5142).\">https://t.me/eduuz/5142).</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">✔️ Endilikda ushbu murojaat