rida XXXII yozgi Olimpiya o&lsquo;yinlari bo&lsquo;lib o&lsquo;tmoqda.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">23 iyul kuni Yaponiyaning Tokio shahrida XXXII yozgi Olimpiya o&lsquo;yinlari rasman ochildi. Ushbu nufuzli musobaqada Vatanimiz sharafini 17 ta sport turidan jami 71 nafar sportchimiz himoya qilmoqda.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Quvonarlisi Vatanimiz sharafini himoya qilayotgan ushbu sportchilarning 27 nafari O&lsquo;zbekiston davlat jismoniy tarbiya va sport universitetining sobiq va hozirda taʼlim olayotgan sportchi talabalari hisoblanishadi. &nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Universitet jamoasi barcha sportchilarimizga omad yor bo&lsquo;lishini tilaydi.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/3.%20%D0%A3%D0%B7%D0%94%D0%96%D0%A2%D0%A1%D0%A3%2008.07..pdf\">https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/3.%20%D0%A3%D0%B7%D0%94%D0%96%D0%A2%D0%A1%D0%A3%2008.07..pdf</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">O&lsquo;zDJTSU matbuot xizmati</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://t.me/uzdjtsu_rasmiy</p>\r\n','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": \"\", \"meta_des_2\": \"\", \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_2\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1627153200,NULL,1627190777,1627190885,270,132,1,1,1627190777,1627190777,1627190777,1627190777),(195,1,'kasbiy-ijodiy-imtihonlar-boshlandi','Kasbiy (ijodiy) imtihonlar boshlandi','','',NULL,NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">2021-2022 o&lsquo;quv yilida universitetga o&lsquo;qishga kirish uchun 7 ta bakalavriat taʼlim yo&lsquo;nalishlariga 10578 nafar abituriyentlar hujjati ro&lsquo;yxatdan o&lsquo;tkazilgan.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Maktabgacha va boshlang&lsquo;ich taʼlimda jismoniy tarbiya va sport hamda Sport faoliyati (faoliyat turlari bo&lsquo;yicha) bakalavriat taʼlim yo&lsquo;nalishida kasbiy (ijodiy) imtihonlar joriy yilning 25 iyuldan 7 avgust kuniga qadar hududlar kesimida hamda sport turlari bo&lsquo;yicha bo&lsquo;lib o&lsquo;tadi.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Imtihonlar o&lsquo;tkazilishidan uch kun oldin abituriyentlar ro&lsquo;yxatdan o&lsquo;tish vaqtida ko&lsquo;rsatgan telefon raqamiga SMS xabarnoma yuborilib, ularga imtihon o&lsquo;tkazish sanasi, joyi va vaqti haqida maʼlum qilingan.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Bugun Andijon viloyatidan ro&lsquo;yxatdan o&lsquo;tgan 307 nafar sportchi abituriyentlardan jami 201 nafari kasbiy (ijodiy) imtihonlarni topshirish uchun yetib keldi. Shuningdek, tennis va eshkak eshish yo&lsquo;nalishlari bo&lsquo;yicha hududlardan jami 448 nafar abituriyentlar ro&lsquo;yxatdan o&lsquo;tgan bo&lsquo;lib, shundan, 267 nafari maxsus texnik jismoniy tayyorgarlik va umumiy jismoniy tayyorgarlik bo&lsquo;yicha sinovlarda ishtirok etdi.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Uzrli sabablarga ko&lsquo;ra yetib kelmagan abituriyentlarga zaxira kunlarda imtihonlarni topshirishga ruxsat beriladi.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Xolislik va shaffoflikni taʼminlash maqsadida har bir imtihon o&lsquo;tkazish joyi kuzatuv kameralari bilan jihozlandi. imtihon jarayonlari videokameralar orqali yozib olinmoqda va zarur bo&lsquo;lgan holatda ushbu video tasvirlarni ko&lsquo;rish imkoni mavjud.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Shuningdek, imtihonlarni adolatli va haqqoniy o&lsquo;tishini taʼminlash maqsadida imtihon oluvchi komissiya aʼzolari safiga sport federatsiyalaridan, huquqni muhofaza qiluvchi organlaridan mutaxassislar taklif etilgan. Ko&lsquo;p yillik tajribaga ega sport mutaxassislari jamoasi kasbiy (ijodiy) imtihon jarayonlarini odilona o&lsquo;tkazishmoqda.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Shu bilan birga kasbiy (ijodiy) imtihonlar jarayonini kuzatib borish uchun xalq deputatlari va jamoatchilik kengashi aʼzolari biriktirilgan.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Eng asosiysi ijodiy imtihonlarni o&lsquo;tkazishda karantin qoidalariga qatʼiy ravishda amal qilingan holda har bir abituriyent normativ hujjatlarda belgilanganidek ichimlik suvi, tibbiyot niqobi va qo&lsquo;lqopi bilan taʼminlanmoqda.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Universitetda abituriyentlar uchun qator qulayliklar, jumladan kasbiy (ijodiy) imtihon dasturi haqida maʼlumotlar va tavsiyalar berish hamda ularni qiziqtirgan savollariga tezkor javob berish maqsadida&nbsp; Call-center xizmati faoliyat ko&lsquo;rsatib kelmoqda.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Barcha abituriyentlarga omadlar tilab qolamiz.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>O&lsquo;zDJTSU matbuot xizmati</strong></span></p>\r\n','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": \"\", \"meta_des_2\": \"\", \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_2\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1627153200,NULL,1627204423,1627283972,276,332,1,1,1627204423,1627204423,1627204423,1627204423),(196,39,'onlayn','Jonli efir','Онлайн трансляция','Online broadcast',NULL,NULL,'<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://imtihon.edu.uz/Toshkent/86\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/icons/210728-110558.png\" width=\"480\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n','<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://imtihon.edu.uz/Toshkent/86\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/icons/210728-110558.png\" width=\"480\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n','<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://imtihon.edu.uz/Toshkent/86\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/icons/210728-110558.png\" width=\"480\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo_2021-07-28_10-47-52.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1627447419,NULL,1627447419,1627474676,NULL,0,1,1,1627447419,1627447419,1627447419,1627447419),(197,1,'o-zdjtsu-rahbariyati-chempionning-onasi-va-yaqinlarini-tabriklashdi','O‘zDJTSU rahbariyati chempionning onasi va yaqinlarini tabriklashdi','Руководство  УзГУФКС  поздравило  маму и  близких  чемпиона','The authority of Uzbek state university of physical education and sport congratulate the champion\'s mother and relatives',NULL,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Habaringiz bor 3 avgust kuni hamyurtimiz Akbar Jo&lsquo;rayev Tokio-2020 Olimpiya o&lsquo;yinlarida O&lsquo;zbekistonga ikkinchi oltin medalni keltirdi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Akbar Jo&lsquo;rayev O&lsquo;zbekiston davlat jismoniy tarbiya va sport universiteti2-bosqich talabasi hisoblanadi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Akbar Jo&lsquo;rayev 109 kg vazn toifasida dast ko&lsquo;tarish (193 kg) va siltab ko&lsquo;tarish (237 kg) mashqlarida jami 430 kg.ni o&lsquo;ziga bo&lsquo;ysundirgan holda rekord o&lsquo;rnatib, Olimpiada chempioniga aylandi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Bugun O&lsquo;zbekiston davlat jismoniy tarbiya va sport universiteti rektori, professor Mahmudjon Boltabayev, universitet prorektori Kamil Bayazitov, universitet huzuridagi&nbsp;Jismoniy tarbiya va sport&nbsp;ilmiy tadqiqotlar instituti direktori Rashid Matkarimov va boshqalar chempion talabani tabriklash uchun uning uyiga borib, onasi va yaqinlarini tabriklashdi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Shuningdek, Akbar Jo&lsquo;rayev o&lsquo;qigan umumtaʼlim maktabda bo&lsquo;lib, chempionning maktab o&lsquo;quvchisi bo&lsquo;lgan davrlari eslandi hamda ustozlariga minnatdorchilik izhor qilindi. &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;<strong>O&lsquo;zDJTSU</strong><strong> matbuot xizmati</strong></span></p>\r\n','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Как известно, 3 августа наш соотечественник Акбар Джураев принес Узбекистану вторую золотую медаль на Олимпийских играх в Токио-2020.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Акбар&nbsp; Джураев&nbsp;&nbsp; является&nbsp; студентом 2-го курса Узбекского государственного университета физической культуры и спорта.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Акбар Джураев в общей сложности 109 кг в рывке&nbsp; (193 кг) и рывке (237 кг) в общей сложности 430 кг, покорив его, он установил рекорд и стал олимпийским чемпионом.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Сегодня ректор Узбекского государственного университета физической культуры и спорта, профессор &nbsp;Махмуджон&nbsp; Болтабаев, проректор университета Камиль&nbsp; Баязитов,&nbsp; директор Научно-исследовательского института физической культуры и спорта при&nbsp; Университете Рашид Маткаримов&nbsp; и другие отправились домой, чтобы поздравить чемпиона, поздравили его мать и близких.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Кроме того, в общеобразовательной школе,&nbsp; где учился&nbsp; Акбар&nbsp; Джураев, вспомнили период, когда чемпион был школьником, и выразили признательность его наставникам.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Пресс-служба УзГУФКС</span></p>\r\n','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">It is well-known news that the Akbar Juraev get the golden medal of Olympic games Tokyo-2020.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The Akbar Juraev is second year student of the University.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The Akbar Juraev make the world record by pushing (237 kg) and jerking (193) overall he lifted 430 kg.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Today, the rector of Uzbek state university of physical education and sport professor Maxmudjon Boltaboev, the vice-rector Kamil Bayazitov, the director of the scientific research institute Rashid Matkarimov and others&nbsp; went to congratulate the winner&#39;s mother and relatives.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">For instance, it is also visited to the school of winner and expressed thankfulness to winner&#39;s teachers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">the press service of UzSUPhES</span></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"meta_des_0\": \"\", \"meta_des_1\": \"\", \"meta_des_2\": \"\", \"meta_des_3\": null, \"meta_des_4\": null, \"meta_title_0\": null, \"meta_title_1\": null, \"meta_title_2\": null, \"meta_title_3\": null, \"meta_title_4\": null, \"meta_keyword_0\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_1\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_2\": \"\", \"meta_keyword_3\": null, \"meta_keyword_4\": null}',1628017200,NULL,1628076707,1628234665,284,75,1,1,1628076707,1628076707,1628076707,1628076707),(198,1,'diqqat-tanlov','#Diqqat_Tanlov','Внимание! Конкурс!','',NULL,NULL,'<p><strong>#Diqqat_Tanlov</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>O&#39;zbekiston davlat jismoniy tarbiya va sport universitetida tahsil olayotgan talaba-yoshlar o&#39;rtasida O&#39;zbekiston Respublikasi Mustaqilligining 30-yilligiga bag&#39;ishlab nazm yo&#39;nalishi bo&#39;yicha &quot;Vatan madhi&quot; mavzusida onlayn videoroliklar tanlovini e&#39;lon qiladi. Tanlovda barcha istedodli yoshlar she&#39;riy tarzda ijro etilgan videoroliklarini 20-avgust sanasiga qadar @Sardor_Eshpolatov telegram manziliga jo&#39;natishlari mumkin.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://st.jtsu.uz/elfinder-files/%D0%92%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD_%D0%BC%D0%B0%D0%B4%D2%B3%D0%B8_%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%BC_%D0%B9%D1%9E%D0%BD%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%88%D0%B8_%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B2_%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%BC%D0%B8.pdf\">Tanlov nizomi!</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>?</strong><strong>Qani shoshilamiz</strong><strong>?</strong><strong>&zwj;♀</strong><strong>?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Viderolik